dbQuery.sql:
SELECT AL1.LEG_CNTRY_CD , AL1.PID_12 , AL1.PRDHA , AL1.TYPE , AL1.MODL , AL1.TRN_TYPE_CD , AL1.MFR_CD , AL1.CALC_ITEM_WEIGHT , SUM(AL1.QTY) AS QTY , 'Monitors' AS WEEE_SUBCAT , UCASE(AL1.ITEM_DESC) AS ITEM_DESC , AL1.PROD_DESC , Current_Date AS RUNDATE , AL1.CASE_KEY , AL1.INVOICE_DATE , AL1.INVOICE_TYPE_CD , AL1.SHIP_FROM_CNTRY_CD , AL1.SHIP_FROM_LOC_CD , AL1.SHIP_TO_CNTRY_CD , AL1.SHIP_TO_LOC_CD , AL1.LAST_UPDT_DATE , AL1.PRODDIV_CD , AL1.PRODDIV_GRP_CD , AL1.PROD_CAT , AL1.PROD_BRAND , AL1.HS_CODE , AL1.DTCN_CUSTNO , AL1.INV_NBR , CASE WHEN AL1.TRN_TYPE_CD ='I' THEN AL1.VAT_ID_BUYI WHEN AL1.TRN_TYPE_CD ='E' THEN AL1.VAT_ID_SELI WHEN AL1.TRN_TYPE_CD='H' AND AL1.MFR_CD='M' THEN AL1.VAT_ID_SELI END AS VATID , AL1.PRODUCT_CODE , AL1.INV_CNTRY_CD , AL1.INV_LOC_CD , AL1.INV_VENDOR ,AL1.INV_TO_CNTRY_CD ,AL1.INV_TO_LOC_CD ,AL1.INV_TO_VENDOR ,AL1.SHIP_TO_NAME FROM WSDIW.PL_ITEM_PRDHA AL1 WHERE Substr(HS_CODE,1,4) ='8528' AND AL1.INVOICE_DATE BETWEEN #prompt('p_StartInvoiceDate','Date''1999-01-01''','current_date')# and #prompt('p_EndInvoiceDate','Date''1999-01-01''','current_date')# AND AL1.LEG_CNTRY_CD IN (#promptmany('p_LCC')#) GROUP BY AL1.LEG_CNTRY_CD , AL1.PID_12 , AL1.TYPE , AL1.MODL , AL1.TRN_TYPE_CD , AL1.MFR_CD , AL1.PRDHA , AL1.CALC_ITEM_WEIGHT , AL1.PRDHA , AL1.ITEM_DESC , AL1.PROD_DESC , AL1.CASE_KEY , AL1.INVOICE_DATE , AL1.INVOICE_TYPE_CD , AL1.SHIP_FROM_CNTRY_CD , AL1.SHIP_FROM_LOC_CD , AL1.SHIP_TO_CNTRY_CD , AL1.SHIP_TO_LOC_CD , AL1.LAST_UPDT_DATE , AL1.PRODDIV_CD , AL1.PRODDIV_GRP_CD , AL1.PROD_CAT , AL1.PROD_BRAND , AL1.HS_CODE , AL1.DTCN_CUSTNO , AL1.INV_NBR , CASE WHEN AL1.TRN_TYPE_CD ='I' THEN AL1.VAT_ID_BUYI WHEN AL1.TRN_TYPE_CD ='E' THEN AL1.VAT_ID_SELI WHEN AL1.TRN_TYPE_CD='H' AND AL1.MFR_CD='M' THEN AL1.VAT_ID_SELI END , AL1.PRODUCT_CODE , AL1.INV_CNTRY_CD , AL1.INV_LOC_CD , AL1.INV_VENDOR ,AL1.INV_TO_CNTRY_CD ,AL1.INV_TO_LOC_CD ,AL1.INV_TO_VENDOR ,AL1.SHIP_TO_NAME
UNION ALL
SELECT AL1.LEG_CNTRY_CD , AL1.PID_12 , AL1.PRDHA , AL1.TYPE , AL1.MODL , AL1.TRN_TYPE_CD , AL1.MFR_CD , AL1.CALC_ITEM_WEIGHT , Sum(AL1.QTY) AS QTY , 'Printers' AS WEEE_SUBCAT , UCASE(AL1.ITEM_DESC) AS ITEM_DESC , AL1.PROD_DESC , Current_Date AS RUNDATE , AL1.CASE_KEY , AL1.INVOICE_DATE , AL1.INVOICE_TYPE_CD , AL1.SHIP_FROM_CNTRY_CD , AL1.SHIP_FROM_LOC_CD , AL1.SHIP_TO_CNTRY_CD , AL1.SHIP_TO_LOC_CD , AL1.LAST_UPDT_DATE , AL1.PRODDIV_CD , AL1.PRODDIV_GRP_CD , AL1.PROD_CAT , AL1.PROD_BRAND , AL1.HS_CODE , AL1.DTCN_CUSTNO , AL1.INV_NBR ,CASE WHEN AL1.TRN_TYPE_CD ='I' THEN AL1.VAT_ID_BUYI WHEN AL1.TRN_TYPE_CD ='E' THEN AL1.VAT_ID_SELI WHEN AL1.TRN_TYPE_CD='H' AND AL1.MFR_CD='M' THEN AL1.VAT_ID_SELI END AS VATID , AL1.PRODUCT_CODE , AL1.INV_CNTRY_CD , AL1.INV_LOC_CD , AL1.INV_VENDOR ,AL1.INV_TO_CNTRY_CD ,AL1.INV_TO_LOC_CD ,AL1.INV_TO_VENDOR ,AL1.SHIP_TO_NAME FROM WSDIW.PL_ITEM_PRDHA AL1 WHERE Substr(HS_CODE,1,4) ='8443' AND AL1.INVOICE_DATE BETWEEN #prompt('p_StartInvoiceDate','Date''1999-01-01''','current_date')# and #prompt('p_EndInvoiceDate','Date''1999-01-01''','current_date')# AND AL1.LEG_CNTRY_CD IN (#promptmany('p_LCC')#) GROUP BY AL1.LEG_CNTRY_CD , AL1.PID_12 , AL1.TYPE , AL1.MODL , AL1.TRN_TYPE_CD , AL1.MFR_CD , AL1.CALC_ITEM_WEIGHT , AL1.PRDHA , AL1.ITEM_DESC , AL1.PROD_DESC , AL1.CASE_KEY , AL1.INVOICE_DATE , AL1.INVOICE_TYPE_CD , AL1.SHIP_FROM_CNTRY_CD , AL1.SHIP_FROM_LOC_CD , AL1.SHIP_TO_CNTRY_CD , AL1.SHIP_TO_LOC_CD , AL1.LAST_UPDT_DATE , AL1.PRODDIV_CD , AL1.PRODDIV_GRP_CD , AL1.PROD_CAT , AL1.PROD_BRAND , AL1.HS_CODE , AL1.DTCN_CUSTNO , AL1.INV_NBR , CASE WHEN AL1.TRN_TYPE_CD ='I' THEN AL1.VAT_ID_BUYI WHEN AL1.TRN_TYPE_CD ='E' THEN AL1.VAT_ID_SELI WHEN AL1.TRN_TYPE_CD='H' AND AL1.MFR_CD='M' THEN AL1.VAT_ID_SELI END , AL1.PRODUCT_CODE , AL1.INV_CNTRY_CD , AL1.INV_LOC_CD , AL1.INV_VENDOR ,AL1.INV_TO_CNTRY_CD ,AL1.INV_TO_LOC_CD ,AL1.INV_TO_VENDOR ,AL1.SHIP_TO_NAME
UNION ALL
SELECT AL1.LEG_CNTRY_CD , AL1.PID_12 , AL1.PRDHA , AL1.TYPE , AL1.MODL , AL1.TRN_TYPE_CD , AL1.MFR_CD , AL1.CALC_ITEM_WEIGHT , Sum(AL1.QTY) AS QTY , 'IT Others' AS WEEE_SUBCAT , UCASE(AL1.ITEM_DESC) AS ITEM_DESC , AL1.PROD_DESC , Current_Date AS RUNDATE , AL1.CASE_KEY , AL1.INVOICE_DATE , AL1.INVOICE_TYPE_CD , AL1.SHIP_FROM_CNTRY_CD , AL1.SHIP_FROM_LOC_CD , AL1.SHIP_TO_CNTRY_CD , AL1.SHIP_TO_LOC_CD , AL1.LAST_UPDT_DATE , AL1.PRODDIV_CD , AL1.PRODDIV_GRP_CD , AL1.PROD_CAT , AL1.PROD_BRAND , AL1.HS_CODE , AL1.DTCN_CUSTNO , AL1.INV_NBR , CASE WHEN AL1.TRN_TYPE_CD ='I' THEN AL1.VAT_ID_BUYI WHEN AL1.TRN_TYPE_CD ='E' THEN AL1.VAT_ID_SELI WHEN AL1.TRN_TYPE_CD='H' AND AL1.MFR_CD='M' THEN AL1.VAT_ID_SELI END AS VATID , AL1.PRODUCT_CODE , AL1.INV_CNTRY_CD , AL1.INV_LOC_CD , AL1.INV_VENDOR ,AL1.INV_TO_CNTRY_CD ,AL1.INV_TO_LOC_CD ,AL1.INV_TO_VENDOR ,AL1.SHIP_TO_NAME FROM WSDIW.PL_ITEM_PRDHA AL1 WHERE NOT Substr(HS_CODE,1,4) ='8528'
AND NOT Substr(HS_CODE,1,4) ='8443'
AND AL1.INVOICE_DATE BETWEEN #prompt('p_StartInvoiceDate','Date''1999-01-01''','current_date')# and #prompt('p_EndInvoiceDate','Date''1999-01-01''','current_date')# AND AL1.LEG_CNTRY_CD IN (#promptmany('p_LCC')#) GROUP BY AL1.LEG_CNTRY_CD , AL1.PID_12 , AL1.TYPE , AL1.MODL , AL1.TRN_TYPE_CD , AL1.MFR_CD , AL1.PRDHA , AL1.CALC_ITEM_WEIGHT , AL1.PRDHA , AL1.ITEM_DESC , AL1.PROD_DESC , AL1.CASE_KEY , AL1.INVOICE_DATE , AL1.INVOICE_TYPE_CD , AL1.SHIP_FROM_CNTRY_CD , AL1.SHIP_FROM_LOC_CD , AL1.SHIP_TO_CNTRY_CD , AL1.SHIP_TO_LOC_CD , AL1.LAST_UPDT_DATE , AL1.PRODDIV_CD , AL1.PRODDIV_GRP_CD , AL1.PROD_CAT , AL1.PROD_BRAND , AL1.HS_CODE , AL1.DTCN_CUSTNO , AL1.INV_NBR , CASE WHEN AL1.TRN_TYPE_CD ='I' THEN AL1.VAT_ID_BUYI WHEN AL1.TRN_TYPE_CD ='E' THEN AL1.VAT_ID_SELI WHEN AL1.TRN_TYPE_CD='H' AND AL1.MFR_CD='M' THEN AL1.VAT_ID_SELI END , AL1.PRODUCT_CODE , AL1.INV_CNTRY_CD , AL1.INV_LOC_CD , AL1.INV_VENDOR ,AL1.INV_TO_CNTRY_CD ,AL1.INV_TO_LOC_CD ,AL1.INV_TO_VENDOR ,AL1.SHIP_TO_NAME

Select DISTINCT PL_ITEM_PRDHA.LEG_CNTRY_CD From WSDIW.PL_ITEM_PRDHA as PL_ITEM_PRDHA WHERE PL_ITEM_PRDHA.INVOICE_DATE BETWEEN #prompt('p_StartInvoiceDate','Date''1999-01-01''','current_date')# and #prompt('p_EndInvoiceDate','Date''1999-01-01''','current_date')#

queryItem.name: WEEE Category
queryItem.expression: IF ( [Consolidation View].[Query1].[WEEE SubCat] in ('Printers','Monitors') ) THEN ('B2C') ELSE ('B2B')

queryItem.name: (1) Imported Quantity
queryItem.expression: IF ([Consolidation View].[Query1].[Transaction Type Code] = 'I') THEN ( [Consolidation View].[Query1].[Product Quantity] ) ELSE ( 0 )

queryItem.name: (2) Manufactured Quantity
queryItem.expression: IF (([Consolidation View].[Query1].[Transaction Type Code] = 'H') and ([Consolidation View].[Query1].[Manufacturer CD] = 'M')) THEN ( [Consolidation View].[Query1].[Product Quantity] ) ELSE ( IF (([Consolidation View].[Query1].[Transaction Type Code] = 'E') and ([Consolidation View].[Query1].[Manufacturer CD] = 'M')) THEN ( [Consolidation View].[Query1].[Product Quantity] ) ELSE ( 0 ) )

queryItem.name: (3) Exported Quantity
queryItem.expression: IF ( [Consolidation View].[Query1].[Transaction Type Code] = 'E') THEN ( [Consolidation View].[Query1].[Product Quantity] ) ELSE ( 0 )

queryItem.name: Total Quantity (1)+(2)-(3)
queryItem.expression: [Consolidation View].[Query1].[(1) Imported Quantity] + [Consolidation View].[Query1].[(2) Manufactured Quantity] - [Consolidation View].[Query1].[(3) Exported Quantity]

queryItem.name: (1) Imported Weight (kg)
queryItem.expression: [Consolidation View].[Query1].[(1) Imported Quantity] * [Consolidation View].[Query1].[Calc Item Weight]

queryItem.name: (2) Manufactured Weight (kg)
queryItem.expression: [Consolidation View].[Query1].[(2) Manufactured Quantity] * [Consolidation View].[Query1].[Calc Item Weight]

queryItem.name: (3) Exported Weight (kg)
queryItem.expression: [Consolidation View].[Query1].[(3) Exported Quantity] * [Consolidation View].[Query1].[Calc Item Weight]

queryItem.name: Total Weight (kg) (1)+(2)-(3)
queryItem.expression: [Consolidation View].[Query1].[(1) Imported Weight (kg)] + [Consolidation View].[Query1].[(2) Manufactured Weight (kg)] - [Consolidation View].[Query1].[(3) Exported Weight (kg)]

queryItem.name: Sort Order
ProddivInd
queryItem.expression: IF( [Consolidation View].[Query1].[Product Division Code] = '' ) THEN ('blank') ELSE ('nonblank')
